  24 Aug 2007; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  brasero-0.6.0.ebuild:
  ppc stable, bug #189991

  24 Aug 2007; <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Fix USE=libnotify on the ebuild. Thanks to Nirbheek Chauhan
  <nirbheek.chauhan@gmail.com> on Bug #189779.

  29 Jul 2007; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  brasero-0.5.2.ebuild:
  ppc stable, bug #185630

  25 Jul 2007; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.2.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug 185630

  19 Jul 2007; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #185630

  17 Jul 2007; <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.2.ebuild,
  -brasero-0.5.90.ebuild, brasero-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Properly install gconf schema. Closes bug #174662 thanks to 
  Luca Marturana <lucamarturana@gmail.com>. Removed older 
  versions.

*brasero-0.6.0 (11 Jul 2007)
*brasero-0.5.90 (11 Jul 2007)

  11 Jul 2007; Steve Dibb <beandog@gentoo.org> +brasero-0.5.90.ebuild,
  +brasero-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Version bump

  08 Apr 2007; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc for bug #168560.

*brasero-0.5.2 (27 Feb 2007)

  27 Feb 2007; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> +brasero-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Version Bump. New Homepage. Remove older this is a bug fix release. Drop
  ~ppc keyword due libisofs lack of keyword for this arch.

  24 Jan 2007; Marius Mauch <genone@gentoo.org> brasero-0.4.4.ebuild,
  brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Replacing einfo with elog

  13 Jan 2007; nixnut <nixnut@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc wrt bug 156453

  27 Nov 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Added libburn support and remove libnotify since it won't be used by this
  stable series. Drop ~ppc keyword because libburn needs to be keyworded.

  18 Nov 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Use gnome-mount instead of pmount fixes bug #155569.

*brasero-0.5.1 (15 Nov 2006)

  15 Nov 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> +brasero-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Version Bump. Closes bug #152214.

  04 Nov 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> -brasero-0.4.2.ebuild,
  brasero-0.4.4.ebuild, brasero-0.4.90.ebuild:
  Remove older version. Added gstreamer ffmpeg plugin to depend fixes bug
  #146835.

  17 Sep 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.4.2.ebuild,
  brasero-0.4.4.ebuild, brasero-0.4.90.ebuild:
  Added vitual/cdrtools as dependency.

*brasero-0.4.4 (07 Sep 2006)

  07 Sep 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> +brasero-0.4.4.ebuild:
  Version Bump of stable release that works with nautilus-burn 2.16.

*brasero-0.4.90 (06 Sep 2006)

  06 Sep 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> +brasero-0.4.90.ebuild:
  Version Bump. This version is the development releases for 0.5.0 stable.

  04 Sep 2006; Luis Medinas <metalgod@gentoo.org> brasero-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Added cdrdao dependency thanks to Arif Lukito <maxima.bugs@gmail.com> on bug
  #145173.

*brasero-0.4.2 (04 Sep 2006)

